    This class represents a Csv_meta_data that contains data about a gps point besides for it's coordinates. If the list has only two Arrays: it represents the data of an element with one Array for titles and one for data. If the list has more than two Arrays: it represents the data of a layer with one Array for titles and the rest for data. If the list has more than two Arrays and contains Arrays with "\n": it represents the data of a project with one Array for titles the rest for data and the "\n" Array separates the different layers.
